    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a good start. for the \"dress codes\" and \"dining etiquette\" parts, can u give me some specific examples of what someone should wear or how they should act to come across as the most polished and professional? like, what's the gold standard for looking high-class in a global business setting?",
