      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For the gold standard in global business, aim for impeccable, understated tailoring in neutral tones like charcoal or navy, regardless of the region. Men should favor high-quality, well-fitted suits with silk ties, while women should opt for sophisticated, structured separates or elegant, conservative dresses. In dining, always observe the host's lead, use the correct silverware from the outside in, and never speak with your mouth full, maintaining an air of quiet, confident composure at all times.",
